Class ICommand.KeyValuePair

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.mobius.vdrapi.command.ICommand.KeyValuePair
Enclosing class:
ICommand
public static class ICommand.KeyValuePair
extends Object

Represents key value pairs used as parameters to the ICommand.load(java.util.Vector) function. In each command object, parameters are passed in the form <KEY> <VALUE>. Each one of these pairs can be represented with this class.
